    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered coupe. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six benefits from a recently overhauled double VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring the longevity of its 8,000 RPM ceiling. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. To address known chassis weak points, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The suspension features upgraded poly-bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for improved turn-in and lateral stability. While the aesthetics reflect a well-loved driver\u2019s car with minor road patina, the drivetrain remains tight and the individual throttle bodies offer the signature induction roar and razor-sharp response enthusiasts crave.",
      "price": 34500.0,
