      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been treated with care. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel rim\u2014typical for a car of this age. The interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seating is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, backed by a complete service history that documents regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The brakes are firm, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring safety for many miles to come. This is a solid, honest vehicle that drives as well as it looks.",
